#: _versions/3.33/guides/redis-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This feature is especially useful when the application must dynamically select a Redis Client from a predefined set at\n"
"runtime."
msgstr "当应用程序必须在运行时从预定义的集合中动态选择一个 Redis 客户端时，此功能特别有用。"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/redis-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An example of configuring multiple Redis Clients for runtime selection:"
