#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/redis-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Setting `quarkus.redis.one.active=true` xref:config-reference.adoc#configuration-sources[at runtime] makes only the\n"
"Redis Client `one` available.\n"
"Setting `quarkus.redis.two.active=true` at runtime makes only the Redis Client `two` available."
msgstr "xref:config-reference.adoc#configuration-sources[在运行时] 将 `quarkus.redis.one.active 设置为 true` ，将仅使 Redis 客户端 `一` 可用；在运行时将 `quarkus.redis.two.active` 设置 `为 true` ，将仅使 Redis 客户端 `二可用` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/redis-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A Redis Client (either default or named) must always be discoverable at build-time to be considered for runtime\n"
"injection. This can be done by injecting the Redis Client name with `@RedisClientName`. If the Redis Client name may be\n"
"active or inactive, it needs to use the wrapper `InjectableInstance<>`, or else Quarkus will throw an exception at\n"
"startup time if the Redis Client is inactive. Alternatively, Redis Clients may also be discovered via configuration."
msgstr "Redis 客户端（无论是默认的还是命名的）必须在构建时始终可被发现，才能被纳入运行时注入的范围。这可以通过使用 `@RedisClientName` 注入 Redis 客户端名称来实现。 如果 Redis 客户端可能处于活动或非活动状态，则需要使用 `InjectableInstance<>` 包装器；否则，如果 Redis 客户端处于非活动状态，Quarkus 将在启动时抛出异常。此外，Redis 客户端也可以通过配置进行发现。"

