"This can be configured using `quarkus.redis.max-pool-waiting`."
msgstr "当连接池耗尽时，获取连接的请求会被放入队列中。默认情况下，队列中等待获取 Redis 连接的请求最多为 24 个。可以通过 `quarkus.redis.max-pool-waiting` 进行配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/redis-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Executing certain commands modifies the server-side state and the behavior of the connection.\n"
