#, fuzzy
msgid "The `.redis` file follows a _one command per line_ format:"
msgstr "`.redis` 文件采用 _每行一个命令_ 的格式："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/redis-reference.adoc
